channel.title: Compiler Error
channel.description:
ok i saw someone trying to get help with their skillcapes and i decided why not give it a try to mine. here is the thread i got it off http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,435032.0.html so i did it all and now when i compile i get this error [code]clickingMost.java:594: cannot find symbol symbol : method SkillCape() location: class client c.SkillCape(); ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
does anyone know how to fix this, and yes i added the public void in client.java cuz i think thats where it belongs lol
